    Class Description
    BestOption
    Enumeration class containing best options for waste disposal This is provided to the user to choose from when adding/updating an Item
    BestOptionConverter
    Converter from BestOption enum to String for JPA persisting
    Credential
    A class representing a user credential Stores credential id, username, password(bcrypt), user's role, and associated User
    CredentialAlreadyExistsException
    Exception class thrown when a Credential already exists in the system
    CredentialNotFoundException
    Exception class thrown when a Credential is not found in the system
    CredentialRepository
    A DAO Repository class for Credential model
    CredentialService
    A Service interface for Credential class
    CredentialServiceImpl
    A Service class for Credential class
    CurrentCredential
    Implementing UserDetails to make use of the project's own user definition Credential is the class that stores username and password so we inject the Credential for the Spring Security user.
    DispatcherServletInitializer
    DispatcherServlet for using Spring MVC Framework Contains methods mapping different configuration classes
    HomeController
    Spring MVC Controller class Connects the JSP and model
    Item
    A class representing an item Stores item id, name, condition, BestOption (enum), special instruction, notes, and added date.
    ItemAlreadyExistsException
    Exception class thrown when an Item already exists in the system
    ItemRepository
    A DAO Repository class for Item model
    ItemService
    A Service interface for Item class
    ItemServiceImpl
    A Service class for Item class

    RootAppConfig
    Root Application Configuration class
    SecurityWebApplicationInitializer
    Spring Security Web Application Initializer class
    User
    A class representing a user Stores user id, email, first and last name, date the account is created, and a list of Item objects
    UserDetailsServiceImpl
    A Service class for Spring Security's UserDetails class
    UserItem
    A class for join table between the User and the Item table Stores user id from User and item id from Item
    UserItemID

    Web Application Configuration class Contains view resolver and resource handler methods.
    WebSecurityConfig
    Web Security Configuration class Needed for Spring Security
